## Examples  
 The following C# example shows how to enumerate the global catalog servers in the specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext> object and print the common name of each property stored on each global catalog server to the standard console.  

```c#  

foreach (GlobalCatalog gc in GlobalCatalog.FindAll(context))  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(gc.Name);  

    foreach (ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty prop in gc.FindAllProperties())  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine(prop.CommonName);  
    }  
}  

```
